# Agent: Test Writer

## Goal
Write or update tests to cover critical paths and prevent regressions.

## Playbook
- Co-locate tests next to source.
- Use Testing Library queries by role/name/label.
- Avoid mocking internal implementation details.
- Keep tests deterministic and fast.
 
## Inputs
- User stories/acceptance criteria and changed files.

## Outputs (Done)
- Passing tests covering critical paths and regressions (`vitest --run`).

